long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tensity Diagrammer is a tool for drawing, or mapping out interconnected spaces. You define the graph by intersections between objects.  It can be used to quickly visualize the interconnections between the activities of your life, or the pros and cons of a decision, or just making some fun shapes online.
